OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FWater companies could now face new
OL,7,Flegal challenges over sewage
OL,8,Fdischarges, campaigners have said,
OL,9,Ffollowing a "landmark" Supreme Court
OL,10,Fruling.
OL,12,FThe judgment, by seven justices of the
OL,13,FUK's highest court, enables the
OL,14,FManchester Ship Canal Company (MSCC),
OL,15,Fwhich owns the waterway of the same
OL,16,Fname, to sue United Utilities over
OL,17,Falleged discharges of contaminated
OL,18,Fwater into the canal.
