OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FIt overturns previous rulings from the
OL,7,FHigh Court and Court of Appeal, where
OL,8,Fjudges had said the canal company
OL,9,Fcould not bring legal action for
OL,10,Ftrespass or nuisance.
OL,12,FCampaigners now say the decision could
OL,13,Fnow allow other water companies to
OL,14,Fface legal action over sewage
OL,15,Fdischarges.
OL,17,FIt comes after a long-running dispute
OL,18,Fbetween MSCC and United Utilities
OL,19,Faround discharges of foul water
OL,20,Fcontaminated with untreated sewage
OL,21,Finto the canal.
