OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FThe canal runs for more than 35 miles
OL,7,Ffrom just east of Salford Quays to the
OL,8,FMersey Estuary at Eastham on the
OL,9,FWirral.
OL,11,FThe United Utilities sewerage network
OL,12,Fincludes around 100 outfalls from
OL,13,Fwhich material emanating from sewers,
OL,14,Fsewage treatment works and pumping
OL,15,Fstations is discharged into the water.
