OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FWhen operating within its hydraulic
OL,7,Fcapacity, the discharges are of
OL,8,Fsurface water or treated effluent, but
OL,9,Fwhen the system's hydraulic capacity
OL,10,Fis exceeded at least some foul water
OL,11,Fis discharged.
OL,13,FIt had previously been ruled by the
OL,14,FHigh Court and Court of Appeal that
OL,15,Fwater companies could not be sued by
OL,16,Fprivate individuals or businesses over
OL,17,Fsewage dumping, so MSCC took an appeal
OL,18,Fagainst those rulings to the Supreme
OL,19,FCourt.
