OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FOn social media, former singer Feargal
OL,7,FSharkey, who now campaigns against
OL,8,Fpollution described the ruling as
OL,9,F"massive" adding that it "opens the
OL,10,Fway for 1,000s of claims by fishing
OL,11,Fclubs, swimmers, riparian owners
OL,12,Fagainst water companies".
OL,14,FDuring a two day hearing in March
OL,15,F2023, the court was asked to decide
OL,16,Fwhether MSCC, which owns the beds and
OL,17,Fbanks of the canal, could bring a
OL,18,Fclaim in nuisance or trespass when the
OL,19,Fcanal is polluted by discharges of
OL,20,Ffoul water from outfalls, which are
OL,21,Fmaintained by United Utilities.
