OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FIn its ruling on Tuesday 2 July 2024,
OL,7,FThe Supreme Court unanimously allowed
OL,8,Fthe Canal Company's appeal.
OL,10,FIt holds that the 1991 Act does not
OL,11,Fprevent the Canal Company from
OL,12,Fbringing a claim in nuisance or
OL,13,Ftrespass when the canal is polluted by
OL,14,Fdischarges of foul water from United
OL,15,FUtilities' outfalls, even if there has
OL,16,Fbeen no negligence or deliberate
OL,17,Fmisconduct.
