OL,6,FThe Environmental Law Foundation, a
OL,7,Fcharity which intervened in the
OL,8,FSupreme Court hearing in March,
OL,9,Fwelcomed the ruling.
OL,11,FIts co-director and casework manager,
OL,12,FEmma Montlake, said: "This was a
OL,13,F'monster case' as characterised by
OL,14,Flead counsel for the Manchester Ship
OL,15,FCanal.
OL,17,F"Enormously complex, the outcome has
OL,18,Fthe potential to be a game-changer for
OL,19,Fcommunities up and down the land.
