OL,6,F"Our water environments have been
OL,7,Fregularly polluted with untreated
OL,8,Fsewage, water biodiversity denuded and
OL,9,Fdegraded with impunity by private
OL,10,Fwater companies.
OL,12,F"A national scandal doesn't come close
OL,13,Fto describing what we have put up
OL,14,Fwith. This is a glad day for
OL,15,Fenvironmental justice, not just for
OL,16,Fthe public, but for nature."
