OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FThe Good Law Project, which supported
OL,7,Fthe Environmental Law Foundation,
OL,8,Fdescribed the judgment as a "landmark"
OL,9,Fdecision.
OL,11,FJennine Walker, the group's interim
OL,12,Fhead of legal, said: "This is a
OL,13,Fsensational victory and a real boost
OL,14,Fto the clean-up of our rivers,
OL,15,Fwaterways and seas.
OL,17,F"It gives people stronger legal tools
OL,18,Fto turn the tide on the sewage scandal
OL,19,Fand hold water companies to account,
OL,20,Fafter our toothless and underfunded
OL,21,Fregulators have failed to do so."
