OL,6,FA United Utilities spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We are considering the implications
OL,8,Fof the Supreme Court's ruling and the
OL,9,Fclarification of the circumstances in
OL,10,Fwhich private owners could bring
OL,11,Fproceedings in respect of discharges.
OL,13,F"We understand and share people's
OL,14,Fconcerns about the need for change and
OL,15,Fwe have already made an early start on
OL,16,Fan ambitious proposed #3 billion
OL,17,Fprogramme to improve over 400 storm
OL,18,Foverflows across the North West which
OL,19,Fwould cut spills by 60% over the
OL,20,Fdecade to 2030.
